casebody.data:
No. 10-6403. Thelma Williams, Jr., Petitioner v. Correctional Officer Hardin, et al. 562 U.S. 1039, 131 S. Ct. 603, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 8943.

178 L. Ed. 2d 430,

November 15, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
